.TH gitcmdb 1 "$(date +%Y-%m-%d)" "GitCMDB" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
gitcmdb \- Git-backed configuration management database CLI
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B gitcmdb
.RI " [" command "]"
.SH DESCRIPTION
GitCMDB provides a set of shell utilities to manage infrastructure state stored as JSON documents and versioned by Git.
